name: Cppagent
body:
## MTConnect C++ Agent
The C++ Agent is the reference implementation of the MTConnect Agent for the MTConnect standard.

### Windows Binary Downloads
Github has stopped providing storage for binary downloads. Downloads will from now on be referenced here.

#### Latest
[C++ Agent Version 1.2.0.19 minimal](https://s3.amazonaws.com/mtconnect-agent/cppagent_win32_1.2.0.19_bin_minimal.zip)

[C++ Agent Version 1.2.0.19 full](https://s3.amazonaws.com/mtconnect-agent/cppagent_win32_1.2.0.19_bin.zip)

#### Stable
_Use Latest_
